name: Replenish
description: “Cascades of water descend with the gentle rumble of bass drums. / The hills above are bathed in the coolness of the moon / And covered with a thick robe of clouds, / Above which shine the stars and constellations in their perfect beauty.” — Longchen Rabjam, “Song of the Enchanting Wildwoods”, translated by Timothy Hinkle · 3024×4032 · Rigtsel https://rigtsel.net
